OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury will pray for
OL,4,C'fractured world' on six-day pilgrimage
OL,6,FThe Archbishop of Canterbury said she
OL,7,Fwill have people facing conflict in
OL,8,Fthis "fractured world" on her mind as
OL,9,Fshe walks 87 miles ahead of her
OL,10,Fenthronement as the Church of
OL,11,FEngland's top bishop.
OL,13,FAs well as being the first woman to
OL,14,Fhold the role, Dame Sarah Mullally is
OL,15,Fthe first Archbishop of Canterbury in
OL,16,Fmodern history to undertake the
OL,17,Fpilgrimage.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@VO]
