OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773850286
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury will pray for
OL,4,C'fractured world' on six-day pilgrimage
OL,6,FAlongside her husband Eamonn, she set
OL,7,Foff from St Paul's Cathedral in London
OL,8,Fon Tuesday afternoon, enjoying mild
OL,9,Fweather and bright sunshine for the
OL,10,Ffirst steps of her journey to
OL,11,FCanterbury Cathedral.
OL,13,FWearing walking boots and carrying a
OL,14,Fstaff, the former bishop of London was
OL,15,Fwaved off by cheering schoolchildren
OL,16,Fand tourists in the capital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
