FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773850286
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury will pray for
OL,4,C'fractured world' on six-day pilgrimage
OL,6,FA service of blessing took place in
OL,7,Fthe cathedral's quire before she
OL,8,Fdeparted, with prayers to protect
OL,9,Fthose making the trip being said and
OL,10,FDame Sarah offering up a shell as a
OL,11,Fsymbol of pilgrimage and in thanks for
OL,12,Fthe hospitality of all those
OL,13,Fsupporting her on her journey.
OL,15,FIn an interview just before she set
OL,16,Foff on the six-day walk, she said the
OL,17,Fpilgrimage will be an opportunity both
OL,18,Fto pray and to "encounter people in
OL,19,Fpart of my preparation" to take on her
OL,20,Fnew role in Kent.
OL,26,@zD@POU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
