FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773850286
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury will pray for
OL,4,C'fractured world' on six-day pilgrimage
OL,6,FShe had previously described it as
OL,7,F"deeply humbling to be following in
OL,8,Fthe footsteps of those who have walked
OL,9,Fthis ancient route".
OL,11,FOn Tuesday, asked what might be on her
OL,12,Fmind across the six days, she said:
OL,13,F"It is an opportunity to pray for
OL,14,Fthose people that I encounter.
OL,16,F"But also, obviously, at this moment,
OL,17,Fwe live in a fractured world, so
OL,18,Fpraying for those places where people
OL,19,Fare going to wake up under the threat
OL,20,Fof violence and conflict."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@SO]uD@AOUxD@AOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
