PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773850286
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury will pray for
OL,4,C'fractured world' on six-day pilgrimage
OL,6,FShe added that she will also pray for
OL,7,Fthose in Canterbury "who have been
OL,8,Faffected by meningitis, for all those
OL,9,Faffected by it and those that are
OL,10,Fresponding to it".
OL,12,FA Year 13 pupil in Faversham named
OL,13,Flocally as Juliette Kenny and a
OL,14,Fstudent at the University of Kent have
OL,15,Fdied in the outbreak, with others
OL,16,Ftreated in hospital.
OL,26,@oD@UOUrD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
