PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773850286
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury will pray for
OL,4,C'fractured world' on six-day pilgrimage
OL,6,FAsked if there would be any safety
OL,7,Fmeasures in place for her service of
OL,8,Fenthronement at Canterbury Cathedral
OL,9,Fnext week, she said: "The outbreak of
OL,10,Fmeningitis is being overseen and
OL,11,Fmanaged by the UKHSA (UK Health
OL,12,FSecurity Agency) and clearly we're in
OL,13,Fconversation with them.
OL,15,F"At the moment, there is nothing that
OL,16,Fwe have to put in place. The
OL,17,Fenthronement will go ahead. But, of
OL,18,Fcourse, we're keeping in contact with
OL,19,Fthem."
OL,26,@qD@VOUwD@AOU{D@FO]
