PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773850286
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury will pray for
OL,4,C'fractured world' on six-day pilgrimage
OL,6,FThe journey along the Becket Camino to
OL,7,FCanterbury Cathedral ` during which
OL,8,Fthe Archbishop will stop at various
OL,9,Fpoints for prayer services at
OL,10,Fchurches, cathedrals and abbeys, meet
OL,11,Fother pilgrims and visit schools and
OL,12,Fecumenical organisations ` will end on
OL,13,FMarch 22.
OL,15,FDame Sarah will be formally installed,
OL,16,For enthroned, at Canterbury Cathedral
OL,17,Fon March 25.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
