FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773850286
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury will pray for
OL,4,C'fractured world' on six-day pilgrimage
OL,6,FDame Sarah said she was feeling both
OL,7,Fcalm and a "sense of the unknown" as
OL,8,Fshe set off on the journey.
OL,10,FShe said: "There's something about
OL,11,Fhaving time and space in prayer.
OL,12,FThere's a sense of calmness, but also
OL,13,Fthe sense of the unknown. Who knows
OL,14,Fwhat the next six days will bring?"
OL,16,FStops along her route will include
OL,17,FSouthwark Cathedral, Aylesford Priory,
OL,18,Fthe Shrine of St Jude in Faversham,
OL,19,FLesnes Abbey and Rochester Cathedral.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@aO]rD@KOUvD@cO]
